summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 1732, for the improvement of East 65th Street, in the City of Seattle, from Weedin Place to 15th Avenue Northeast, by grading and curbing the same, and by constructing concrete sidewalks together with wooden cross walks thereon and providing for the necessary surface drainage, under Ordinance No. 18343 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against each parcel of land and part thereof shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof.
